        <button class="w3-btn right" onclick="plusDivs2(+1)">&#10095;</button>
      </div>

      <p>
        First, the internal buoyancy system was prototyped, with the components
        3D printed, laser cut and the reversable motor- pump purchased used.
        Once successful buoyancy variation was achieved, the external hull and
        hydrofoils were prototyped and the whole system assembled. The
        electronic circuit system used to control the motor speed and direction
        was then set up.
      </p>
